---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "Learn about MaiPDF - the secure PDF sharing platform that protects your documents",
	title: "About MaiPDF",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-6">About MaiPDF</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-maipdf max-w-none">
		<p>
			MaiPDF is a revolutionary PDF security platform designed to give you complete control over your document sharing. We understand that sensitive documents need more than just basic password protection - they need comprehensive security that adapts to your specific needs.
		</p>
		<p>Our platform offers advanced security features that set us apart:</p>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>Generate secure sharing links and QR codes for easy access</li>
			<li>Set precise access limits - control how many times your PDF can be viewed</li>
			<li>Implement access control with expiration dates for time-sensitive documents</li>
			<li>Prevent unauthorized copying and printing of your content</li>
			<li>Track access with detailed analytics and monitoring</li>
		</ul>
		<p>
			Whether you're sharing confidential business reports, legal documents, or personal files, MaiPDF ensures your content remains secure while providing the flexibility you need for effective collaboration.
		</p>
		<p>
			Join thousands of professionals who trust MaiPDF to protect their most important documents. <a
				aria-label="get started with MaiPDF"
				class="maipdf-link inline-block"
				href="/"
				rel="noreferrer">Get started today</a> and experience the future of secure document sharing.
		</p>
	</div>

</PageLayout>
